    "dividerPattern": "left-stripe-section-title",
    "motifRationale": "Progressive-disclosure arc with restrained-to-bold accent strategy. The thin accent bar under the title is a recurring 'new argument' signal that scales — narrow on cover/dividers, wider on the closing — without competing with body data content.",
