      "coverExpression": "Thin accent bar (0.05in) sits 0.2in beneath the cover's display title, anchored left.",
      "closingExpression": "Same accent bar widened to 0.12in and run along the slide's bottom edge — visually 'lands' the deck the way the cover bar 'launches' it.",
      "designIntent": "The accent bar is the deck's recurring 'new argument' marker; growing and lowering it on the closing makes the resolution feel earned rather than tacked on."
    }
  },
